- `/bin/cli.ts` - CLI implementation
- `/bin/commands/` - CLI command modules
- `/bin/utils/` - CLI utility functions

## Testing
- `/test/samples/` - Test audio files
- `/test/audiox.test.ts` - Main test suite
- `/test/utils/` - Test utilities

## Documentation
- `/docs/` - VitePress documentation
- `/docs/examples/` - Code examples
